  <releases>
    <release version="v2.5.9" date="2022-10-11">
        <description>
          <p>Assalamou Alaykoum brothers/sisters</p>

          <p>New features:</p>
          <ul>
              <li>Added Russian language.</li>
              <li>New alert sound.</li>
              <li>Default background color is now dark grey (no more flash-bang effect when changing pages).</li>
              <li>Added forward play button in Qur'an (plays from the selected verse until the end).</li>
              <li>Qur'an audio now stops when changing Surahs.</li>
              <li>Added Hijri date corrector.</li>
              <li>Default language and theme are detected on first launch of the app.</li>
              <li>New portable version for Windows (+ new MSI installer).</li>
          </ul>
          <p>BugFixes</p>
          <ul>
              <li>Fixed reload issue at midnight.</li>
          </ul>    
          <p>If there is any problem, please contact me so that I can fix it. If you have any ideas, I'd gladly hear them. Jazzakoum Allahu khairan.</p>
        </description>
      </release>
